 "html": "<div>\n<h3><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-5713 size-full\" src=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/1-1.png\" alt=\"Mustard Sauce\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/1-1.png 640w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-300x300.png 300w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-100x100.png 100w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-600x600.png 600w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-150x150.png 150w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-530x530.png 530w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-500x500.png 500w, /media/uploads/2019/10/1-1-380x380.png 380w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"></h3>\n<h3>Ingredients</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>4 Eggs</li>\n<li>190 ml Vinegar</li>\n<li>2 ml salt</li>\n<li>135 ml  (110g) sugar</li>\n<li>40 ml mustard powder</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><b>Method</b></h3>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ol>\n<li>Whisk everything together in a glass mixing bowl with a balloon whisk.</li>\n<li>Now pour water into an ordinary pot and set the glass bowl on top of the pot of water.</li>\n<li>Bring the water to the boil and stir the contents in the glass bowl constantly. Even though the sauce foams, just keep stirring. It gets nice and thick and looks almost like mayonnaise.</li>\n</ol>\n<div><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-5714 size-full\" src=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/2-2.png\" alt=\"Mustard Sauce\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/2-2.png 640w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-300x300.png 300w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-100x100.png 100w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-600x600.png 600w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-150x150.png 150w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-530x530.png 530w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-500x500.png 500w, /media/uploads/2019/10/2-2-380x380.png 380w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"></div>\n<div>Place in the fridge to get cold. Delicious with pork, on sandwiches or over potato salad.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5712 size-large\" src=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Mustard Sauce\" width=\"530\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-768x1024.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-600x800.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-225x300.jpg 225w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-750x1000.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-380x507.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-760x1013.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36-800x1067.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2019/10/5d208770-0f52-4238-87a1-43a5acb80f36.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\"></div>\n</div>",
